my contact lenses no matter what.

44
00:03:00,540 --> 00:03:01,380
Stop hiding.

45
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:03,700
I can still see you even if you hide.

46
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:06,660
Boss.

47
