51
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:17,620
to you.

52
00:03:18,580 --> 00:03:19,420
Do what?

53
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:22,820
Anyway, I didn't mean it.

54
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:26,060
I couldn't see clearly without my lenses,

55
00:03:26,780 --> 00:03:28,420
so I mistook you.

56
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:29,540
Believe me,

57
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,660
I respect you greatly.

58
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:33,980
I have no improper intentions
towards you.

59
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:38,620
Are you saying

60
00:03:39,620 --> 00:03:41,380
I should thank you
for not being interested in me?

61
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:44,140
That's not what I meant.

62
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:47,180
I offended you first.

63
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:50,540
If you feel uncomfortable,

64
00:03:51,140 --> 00:03:53,940
feel free to make any request.

65
00:03:54,940 --> 00:03:56,180
How could I dare?

66
00:03:58,540 --> 00:04:00,260
I've become Tiger Meng now.

67
00:04:08,620 --> 00:04:09,660
Secretary Chen, morning.

68
00:04:09,740 --> 00:04:10,580
Morning.

69
00:04:12,180 --> 00:04:13,020
Oh my,

70
00:04:13,220 --> 00:04:14,620
what happened to your neck?

71
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,100
Forget it.

72
00:04:18,140 --> 00:04:19,220
I'm having an allergic reaction.

73
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,820
I was on IV drips all night.

74
00:04:20,830 --> 00:04:21,900
I almost had to be hospitalized.

75
00:04:22,260 --> 00:04:23,580
It's that serious?

76
00:04:23,940 --> 00:04:24,700
Get proper treatment.

77
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,810
- (No wonder he didn't come last night.)
- Or you won't find a girlfriend.

78
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:27,400
(He's sick.)

79
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:29,740
(It must be because
he's worried about me,)

80
00:04:30,140 --> 00:04:31,660
(so he asked the boss to come to me.)

81
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:33,660
All because of that
cheap temporary tattoo.

82
00:04:34,620 --> 00:04:35,460
It's fine.

83
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:37,260
Boss said it's covered by

84
00:04:37,940 --> 00:04:38,940
workers' compensation.

85
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:42,380
Ye Ran, you're here.

86
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,860
Could you make me a cup of coffee?

87
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:44,780
I need to use the restroom.

88
00:04:46,060 --> 00:04:46,900
Secretary Chen,

89
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:49,020
