90
00:04:53,900 --> 00:04:54,740
Return it to me?

91
00:04:57,700 --> 00:05:00,220
Ever since you lent me this umbrella
two years ago,

92
00:05:00,740 --> 00:05:02,220
I've had feelings for you.

93
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:03,860
Even though you rejected me yesterday,

94
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:05,780
I won't give up.

95
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:07,980
I hope you can reconsider

96
00:05:08,580 --> 00:05:10,500
and give us both a chance.

97
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:23,380
But this isn't my umbrella.

98
00:05:24,740 --> 00:05:25,600
(2 years ago)
Why are you rushing like

99
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:26,780
you're going to be reincarnated?

100
00:05:27,940 --> 00:05:28,900
Sorry.

101
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:37,700
Secretary Chen,

102
00:05:38,540 --> 00:05:39,420
