to become a real manga artist?

136
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:15,740
There are so many people
who can play the piano,

137
00:08:16,700 --> 00:08:19,820
but not everyone becomes a pianist.

138
00:08:25,500 --> 00:08:26,700
What twisted logic!

139
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:30,940
Just because it's a hobby,

140
00:08:31,860 --> 00:08:34,300
you feel justified

141
00:08:34,700 --> 00:08:35,540
